# shadcn/ui Patterns

## Component Usage

- Use shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui`
- Follow shadcn/ui patterns and conventions
- Use New York style components (as configured in `components.json`)

## Composition Patterns

- Extend shadcn/ui components via composition rather than modification
- Prefer composition over prop drilling
- Create wrapper components when needed for project-specific behavior

## Form Components

- Use shadcn/ui form components when available
- Use React Hook Form with Zod validation
- Create reusable form components
- Handle form errors appropriately with user-friendly messages

## Component Structure

- Keep components small and focused
- Extract reusable logic into custom hooks
- Use meaningful variable and function names
